title: (x) Slab serif fonts used on mileycyrus.com - Rockwell; Courier {Jan E, Lari}
content:
On this page: [http://www.mileycyrus.com/official](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419151326/http:/www.mileycyrus.com/official "http://www.mileycyrus.com/official")

I'm trying to identify the slab serif used for the "miley cyrus \* breakout" text.

Thanks in advance!
author: amills

comments.content: Oh, ‘cyrus’ is Courier, ‘miley’ and ‘breakout’ are Rockwell.
